### Installing manually

To use the Graphlit MCP Server in any MCP client application, use:

```
{
    "mcpServers": {
        "graphlit-mcp-server": {
            "command": "npx",
            "args": [
                "-y",
                "graphlit-mcp-server"
            ],
            "env": {
                "GRAPHLIT_ORGANIZATION_ID": "your-organization-id",
                "GRAPHLIT_ENVIRONMENT_ID": "your-environment-id",
                "GRAPHLIT_JWT_SECRET": "your-jwt-secret",
