```

Optionally, you can configure the credentials for data connectors, such as Slack, Google Email and Notion.
Only GRAPHLIT_ORGANIZATION_ID, GRAPHLIT_ENVIRONMENT_ID and GRAPHLIT_JWT_SECRET are required.
